> Sunhawk fired a laser on each side of he (including up
> and down) to cmpensate for dodging and one straight at
> him.
>

{Nightshade}

    Crouching and bracing herself Nightshade crossed her arms before her
accepting the shot at her, letting the others slip by harmlessly around her,
grunting as the stinging hit scorched the backs of her fore arms. The
glimmer of mirth not once leaving her optic lenses as she regarded the
maximal. "I knew your kind were as bad as the decepticons."
